approved: true
description: <p>Afta Thin is a work in progress. It is a \
  typeface formed of two subfamilies, a Sans and a Serif. \
  Initially conceived to be an Egyptian, it has evolved toward \
  a hybrid of the Humanist, Egyptian and Grotesque genres. \
  This makes it a versatile family that offers readability and \
  elegance. It may be used for body copy and small text thanks to \
  having low contrast and a big body, but it can also be used \
  for headlines because it has a variety of ligatures and details.</p>

